Version - 0.6-pre

    Changed Namespace URNs to use thomasoandrews.com, rather than thomaso.com

Version 0.5

    The Makefile now uses xsltproc, which requires you to install libxml2 and
    libxslt. These can be found at:

        http://www.xmlsoft.org/downloads.html (libxml2)
        http://xmlsoft.org/XSLT/downloads.html (libxslt)

Version 0.4

    Added two articles.

    Added the non-framed DHTML version.

Version 0.3

    Added pre-fetch and shortcut icons to the HTML headers.

    Some basic text improvements to the xml files.

Version 0.2

    Changed to version 2.4 of Xalan.
